[
  {
    "text": "Have to find them.",
    "start": 2.0,
    "duration": 6.559
  },
  {
    "text": "Have to make them pay.",
    "start": 5.359,
    "duration": 5.921
  },
  {
    "text": "There they are.",
    "start": 8.559,
    "duration": 5.921
  },
  {
    "text": "Yuck. Dude, Dino, did you fart for fart?",
    "start": 11.28,
    "duration": 8.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, whoever smelt it dealt it.",
    "start": 14.48,
    "duration": 5.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Dino, why don't you grab some more",
    "start": 21.68,
    "duration": 6.64
  },
  {
    "text": "firewood and give us a breather?",
    "start": 24.08,
    "duration": 7.359
  },
  {
    "text": "Very funny.",
    "start": 28.32,
    "duration": 3.119
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 33.94,
    "duration": 3.13
  },
  {
    "text": "That smell IS DISGUSTING.",
    "start": 39.36,
    "duration": 5.519
  },
  {
    "text": ">> YOU'RE DISGUSTING.",
    "start": 41.84,
    "duration": 6.039
  },
  {
    "text": ">> HUH?",
    "start": 44.879,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Remember me?",
    "start": 48.0,
    "duration": 3.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Me you guys. Guys, you won't believe",
    "start": 60.32,
    "duration": 5.119
  },
  {
    "text": "this.",
    "start": 64.08,
    "duration": 3.84
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Dude, did you forget to wipe?",
    "start": 65.439,
    "duration": 4.881
  },
  {
    "text": ">> This is serious. There's a fifth",
    "start": 67.92,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "monster.",
    "start": 70.32,
    "duration": 6.839
  },
  {
    "text": "Quick, get into the light.",
    "start": 73.04,
    "duration": 4.119
  },
  {
    "text": "Who are you?",
    "start": 81.52,
    "duration": 6.8
  },
  {
    "text": ">> You mean you don't remember me? Sister.",
    "start": 83.92,
    "duration": 7.519
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Sister? What are you talking about? We",
    "start": 88.32,
    "duration": 5.68
  },
  {
    "text": "don't have another brother.",
    "start": 91.439,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": ">> DON'T LIE TO ME.",
    "start": 94.0,
    "duration": 4.159
  },
  {
    "text": ">> The lie. It doesn't work on this",
    "start": 96.079,
    "duration": 2.961
  },
  {
    "text": "monster.",
    "start": 98.159,
    "duration": 4.96
  },
  {
    "text": ">> That's because I'm not a monster. I'm",
    "start": 99.04,
    "duration": 7.6
  },
  {
    "text": "the forgotten child.",
    "start": 103.119,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": "It was a beautiful sunny day. I was",
    "start": 106.64,
    "duration": 6.6
  },
  {
    "text": "taking out the trash like usual.",
    "start": 109.119,
    "duration": 4.121
  },
  {
    "text": ">> You four were there to turn my beautiful",
    "start": 113.36,
    "duration": 5.439
  },
  {
    "text": "day into a waking nightmare.",
    "start": 116.32,
    "duration": 5.439
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Look, guys. P you.",
    "start": 118.799,
    "duration": 5.201
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Hey, skunk kid. Why don't you do us all",
    "start": 121.759,
    "duration": 4.161
  },
  {
    "text": "a favor and throw yourself in there,",
    "start": 124.0,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": "TOO?",
    "start": 125.92,
    "duration": 4.08
  },
  {
    "text": ">> YEAH. Smelly boy. It's where trash like",
    "start": 126.64,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": "you belongs.",
    "start": 130.0,
    "duration": 8.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I don't smell that bad. Do I?",
    "start": 132.64,
    "duration": 5.36
  },
  {
    "text": "You were ruthless. The worst siblings a",
    "start": 141.76,
    "duration": 6.8
  },
  {
    "text": "kid could ask for. Luckily, I had mom.",
    "start": 145.12,
    "duration": 6.759
  },
  {
    "text": ">> It's mom.",
    "start": 148.56,
    "duration": 3.319
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Hi, kids.",
    "start": 155.36,
    "duration": 3.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Who's",
    "start": 166.959,
    "duration": 5.56
  },
  {
    "text": "ready for a camping trip?",
    "start": 168.48,
    "duration": 4.039
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Settle down, kiddos. Hey, Mom. Can I",
    "start": 177.519,
    "duration": 4.401
  },
  {
    "text": "come, too?",
    "start": 180.879,
    "duration": 6.241
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Oh, sweetie. I'd love for you to come,",
    "start": 181.92,
    "duration": 9.599
  },
  {
    "text": "but there's only four extra seats.",
    "start": 187.12,
    "duration": 6.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Plus, nobody wants to be cooped up in a",
    "start": 191.519,
    "duration": 7.561
  },
  {
    "text": "confined space with you, skunk kid.",
    "start": 194.0,
    "duration": 5.08
  },
  {
    "text": "But But",
    "start": 200.48,
    "duration": 7.8
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I'll bring you next time. Okay. Promise.",
    "start": 202.08,
    "duration": 6.2
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I couldn't let myself be left behind.",
    "start": 213.519,
    "duration": 5.961
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Wait for me.",
    "start": 216.08,
    "duration": 3.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, yeah. I'm scared.",
    "start": 230.48,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Me, too. Well,",
    "start": 234.0,
    "duration": 4.239
  },
  {
    "text": ">> don't be. Your mama's handled worse",
    "start": 235.76,
    "duration": 4.559
  },
  {
    "text": "storms than this in her day.",
    "start": 238.239,
    "duration": 4.961
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Yuck. What's that smell? That smells",
    "start": 240.319,
    "duration": 4.161
  },
  {
    "text": "just like",
    "start": 243.2,
    "duration": 3.2
  },
  {
    "text": ">> What's going on out there,",
    "start": 244.48,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Sun?",
    "start": 246.4,
    "duration": 3.6
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Oh, son. What are you doing here? I",
    "start": 247.84,
    "duration": 3.52
  },
  {
    "text": "didn't want TO BE LEFT OUT of all the",
    "start": 250.0,
    "duration": 2.159
  },
  {
    "text": "fun.",
    "start": 251.36,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Great. Now we're going to die and have",
    "start": 252.159,
    "duration": 5.281
  },
  {
    "text": "to smell your stinky butt the whole way",
    "start": 254.64,
    "duration": 8.2
  },
  {
    "text": "down. How could this get any worse?",
    "start": 257.44,
    "duration": 5.4
  },
  {
    "text": "We're going down. Brace yourselves.",
    "start": 269.12,
    "duration": 4.519
  },
  {
    "text": "Mom tried her best, but even the most",
    "start": 275.68,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
    "text": "skilled pilot in the world couldn't stop",
    "start": 278.0,
    "duration": 5.0
  },
  {
    "text": "what was coming.",
    "start": 279.6,
    "duration": 3.4
  },
  {
    "text": "What's that smell?",
    "start": 296.24,
    "duration": 5.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Fire. Dino, koala, squid, KRAKEN. WHERE",
    "start": 298.32,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "ARE YOU GUYS?",
    "start": 302.0,
    "duration": 4.52
  },
  {
    "text": "MOM.",
    "start": 303.52,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "MOM. MOM.",
    "start": 309.52,
    "duration": 3.519
  },
  {
    "text": ">> HUH?",
    "start": 311.6,
    "duration": 3.2
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Skunk kid.",
    "start": 313.039,
    "duration": 3.6
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Hey, let me go.",
    "start": 314.8,
    "duration": 6.399
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Skunk kid, are you out there?",
    "start": 316.639,
    "duration": 7.041
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Can't have any siblings meddling now,",
    "start": 321.199,
    "duration": 4.481
  },
  {
    "text": "can we?",
    "start": 323.68,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Skunk, can you",
    "start": 325.68,
    "duration": 6.48
  },
  {
    "text": "hear me? Huh?",
    "start": 328.4,
    "duration": 5.76
  },
  {
    "text": "What was I doing?",
    "start": 332.16,
    "duration": 3.84
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Sis, get over here.",
    "start": 334.16,
    "duration": 2.96
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Right.",
    "start": 336.0,
    "duration": 5.52
  },
  {
    "text": ">> NO, DON'T LEAVE ME. A cultist took me to",
    "start": 337.12,
    "duration": 6.56
  },
  {
    "text": "their layer, and I was witness to their",
    "start": 341.52,
    "duration": 5.64
  },
  {
    "text": "cruelty firsthand.",
    "start": 343.68,
    "duration": 3.48
  },
  {
    "text": ">> NO. NO. I DON'T WANT THIS. STOP. LET HIM",
    "start": 348.479,
    "duration": 6.801
  },
  {
    "text": "GO.",
    "start": 352.96,
    "duration": 6.84
  },
  {
    "text": "What's happening to me?",
    "start": 355.28,
    "duration": 4.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Let him go. We have a backup.",
    "start": 373.36,
    "duration": 7.88
  },
  {
    "text": ">> What? No. Don't turn me into a monster.",
    "start": 376.16,
    "duration": 5.08
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Proto.",
    "start": 382.479,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "No. Don't make me a monster.",
    "start": 387.919,
    "duration": 4.601
  },
  {
    "text": ">> What? What did you do to me?",
    "start": 396.479,
    "duration": 6.241
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I've given you the means to get your",
    "start": 399.44,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "revenge.",
    "start": 402.72,
    "duration": 2.319
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Revenge?",
    "start": 404.08,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Your siblings, they never cared about",
    "start": 405.039,
    "duration": 5.121
  },
  {
    "text": "you. They mocked you. Made your life",
    "start": 407.44,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "miserable. Don't you remember?",
    "start": 410.16,
    "duration": 7.599
  },
  {
    "text": "Fight. Yes, they must fade. I will get",
    "start": 413.6,
    "duration": 7.48
  },
  {
    "text": "my revenge.",
    "start": 417.759,
    "duration": 3.321
  },
  {
    "text": ">> You know, we really should have better",
    "start": 426.479,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "health insurance.",
    "start": 429.28,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Oh, shut up, Jared.",
    "start": 430.639,
    "duration": 3.921
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Who's Jared?",
    "start": 433.28,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Jared doesn't matter.",
    "start": 434.56,
    "duration": 6.32
  },
  {
    "text": "The point is you will all pay FOR HOW",
    "start": 437.28,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "YOU TREATED ME.",
    "start": 440.88,
    "duration": 3.039
  },
  {
    "text": ">> WAIT,",
    "start": 442.4,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": ">> WHAT? That dust the cultist blew into",
    "start": 443.919,
    "duration": 6.241
  },
  {
    "text": "your face. He did the same to us.",
    "start": 446.88,
    "duration": 4.24
  },
  {
    "text": ">> So",
    "start": 450.16,
    "duration": 5.52
  },
  {
    "text": ">> So it altered our memories. But now I",
    "start": 451.12,
    "duration": 8.04
  },
  {
    "text": "remember everything.",
    "start": 455.68,
    "duration": 3.48
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Look guys, kid needs our help.",
    "start": 460.56,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Hey, bro. Trying to take all the credit,",
    "start": 463.28,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "huh?",
    "start": 465.44,
    "duration": 5.96
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Yeah, silly. Let us help you.",
    "start": 466.0,
    "duration": 5.4
  },
  {
    "text": ">> We love you no matter what.",
    "start": 471.599,
    "duration": 4.561
  },
  {
    "text": "You You do remember me. And I I remember",
    "start": 476.879,
    "duration": 9.681
  },
  {
    "text": "you. The real you, guys. I'm so sorry.",
    "start": 481.44,
    "duration": 5.92
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm sorry.",
    "start": 486.56,
    "duration": 5.319
  },
  {
    "text": ">> We love you no matter what.",
    "start": 487.36,
    "duration": 4.519
  }
]